 />\n豪仔緊係唔委屈啦 <br />\n但豪仔又內向，又唔夠緊貼時事<br />\n以我對大家嘅印象<br />\n在座咁多位都緊貼潮流脈膊<br />\n站起時尚尖端<br />\n我只不過係擔心<br />\n我開口講既野其實所有人<br />\n都一早已經知道姐？<br />\n咁如果係咁 我咪係到發放緊 一啲<br />\n所有人一早接收左既資訊？<br />\n咁唔係唔得，浪費時間呀ma<br />\n再講，我都係多口問句姐<br />\n開場白黎姐，禮儀黎既姐<br />\n唔通我問你食左飯未？<br />\n我真係好想知你食左飯未咩<br />\n我講句早晨，唔通我朝早真係好精神咩<br />\n如果我表達方式令你唔舒服嘅話，<br />\n我可以改呀<br />\n我有無屌你老母臭閪呀<br />\n我無喎<br />\n依家你屌我老母臭閪喎，我好唔舒服呀<br />\n你會唔會改？"},{"pid":"f62441aa0f1a33cc3969d9cdbfa07941952e51f0","tid":2320004,"uid":118346,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08c8258623509a248f40f0fafdff8bbf0033410","tid":2320004,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"似喺邊...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa310856d9c06c985b02ea9ec1d2a1d13c6043b","tid":2320004,"uid":15371,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"你講就柒架啦"},{"pid":"3142d2a06256f542eccde5b4019088f4f62064b2","tid":2320004,"uid":46435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"ok啦 係有少少想和她聖交的fu.."},{"pid":"6c7df6c20e11c3e4d27cc3e94b4a0ccf911c9178","tid":2320004,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fab0e71a985c9ed46bf8c6bbd637584f0de8bf85","tid":2320004,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J51iiwZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ51iiwZ.jpg&h=05a57bf0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n左:yeji 右:creamy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:09:33.000Z","msg":"兩條女好多雀斑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"956afc618a44e76f7fee3e90811e55f6f3b6e12e","tid":2320004,"uid":100227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"似游學